objects.text: Forge Saranac CM is a great crossover bike, innovatively designed for handling a wide range of terrain, from paved pathways to light dirt trails. Powered by front and rear Shimano Altus derailleur and drivetrain with KMC chain and Shimano cassette, Saranac stands alone in overall quality. This Comfort Mountain Series unites the best of both worlds: a quality SR NEX shock in the front fork, WTB Comfort V Comp saddle and seat post suspension, adjustable stem for comfort or performance, an all Aluminum double butted quality frame and 26x1.95" mountain/hybrid tires. Note: Frame size is determined by measuring the distance from the center of the bottom bracket (the bolt that locks in the crank) to the top of the seat tube. Stand-over height is determined by measuring the distance from the ground to the top tube. A bike that you ride only on paved surfaces and never take off road should give you a minimum stand-over height clearance of 2", a bike that you ride on unpaved surfaces should give you a minimum of 3" of stand-over height clearance and a bike that you ride off road should give you a minimum of 4" of stand-over height clearance.

objects.text: Philips Norelco Shaver 6700 gives a soft touch for a smooth shave. GyroFlex 2D contour-following system adjusts seamlessly to every curve of the face, minimizing pressure and irritation. Aquatec Technology allows you to shave wet with gel or foam (in or out of the shower) for extra skin protection or dry for convenience. DualPrecision heads are equipped with slots to shave longer hairs and holes to shave even the shortest stubble. SkinGlide shaving surface slides smoothly over your skin for a close, easy shave. The precision trimmer is perfect for sideburns and moustaches. The Lithium-ion battery delivers 50 minutes of cordless shaving after a 1 hour charge. A 3 minute quick-charge provides enough power for one cordless shave. A 5 level battery indicator ensures you always know how much power is left. Shaver 6700 comes with a charging stand, a click-on precision trimmer head, a 45 day risk-free trial and a full 2-year warranty. For best results, replace shaving heads with RQ11 replacement heads every 12 months. For a limited time, Shaver 6700 includes a bonus 5-length trimmer attachment as well as a Neutrogena Shave Cream (a 35 value). Packaging includes: electric shaver, charging stand, 5-length trimmer, travel pouch, protective cap, power cord and Neutrogena Shave Cream.
